      <p>Last updated: March 18, 2017</p>
      <p>The Parts Ninja ("us", "we", or "our") operates <%= link_to "www.theparts.ninja", root_path %> (the "Site"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from users of the Site.</p>
